measure_like.name: shipments.shipment_count

queryResponse.sql:
SELECT
    shipper_applications.name  AS "shipper_applications.name",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (((CASE
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_backup'  THEN 'Backup/Published'
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'
WHEN coalesce(shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'spot', true)  THEN 'Spot'

END) = 'Contract')) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_contract_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (((CASE
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_backup'  THEN 'Backup/Published'
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'
WHEN coalesce(shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'spot', true)  THEN 'Spot'

END) = 'Spot')) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_spot_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id = shipments.shipper_application_id
WHERE ((( shipments.created_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -11, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipments.created_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 12, DATEADD('month', -11, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    1
ORDER BY
    2 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
